Chrome version: 83.0.4103.116 - 64 bits

in `@schematics/angular/utility/ast-utils`, the function `insertImport` can generate the following import delarations:

```
insertImport(source, fileToEdit, "symbolName" ,"fileName", false);

//will generate:
import { symbolName } from 'fileName'
```

and ...

```
insertImport(source, fileToEdit, "* as symbolName", "fileName", true);
//note isDefault = true (the last parameter)

//will generate:
import * as symbolName from 'fileName'
```

but if there is no symbolName it should remove 'from'
```
insertImport(source, fileToEdit, '', "fileName");

//should generate:
import  'fileName';

//but it generates:
import from 'fileName';
```
